title: Balsam Bagels
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Fast food, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Fast service bagel shop with a number of veg items labeled, including sandwiches, salads, soups, quiche, biscotti, and pastries; quiche & pastries are not vegan. Has non-dairy margarine and coffee creamer, soy cream cheese, vegan cheese, vegetarian sausage on the menu. Small eat-in area.
